        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 7. Geothelphusa iheya new species. (a) Dorsal view; (b) dorsal view of carpace; (c) ventral side of G1; (d) dorsal side of G1; (e) G2. (a) Paratype, ZRC 2006.0078, male, CL 28.7 mm; (b–e) holotype, RUMF-ZC-148, male, CL 32.6 mm. Scale bars: 10 mm (b); 1 mm (c–e)." ;
